_sText:
Hello everyone

This is a a 60-70% completetion preveiw of my map "Delirium"
It is 100% playable with the exception of a few basic jailbreak elements ie: The weapons in the cells.

You can see my video log here:
http://www.youtube.com/user/shinoteseu

And the feedback Forums here:
http://www.xtremejailbreak.com.au/home/forums/viewtopic.php?f=19&t=3012&start=0
http://www.xtremejailbreak.com.au/home/forums/viewtopic.php?f=19&t=2963

If you have any strong experience in mapping and wish to contribute where possible then add my steam account: Shinoteseu

Please don't add my steam account to give feedback.

This version contains the following:

95% finished gunroom
90% finished pool (known as the grotto)
100% finished kitchen and mess hall (may go back and add anyway)
95% finished deagle toss.
95% finished Time attack
100% finished sewers
80% finished cells
65% finished main room

These are just gauged statistcs though
I may alter things as i see fit.

I still have 2 rooms to go and then i need to build 2 vent systems, and then possibly a series of walkways to intergrate the rooms. Thanks to the underground theme of the map i have no real horizontal or vertical limitations. And by limitations i mean i don't need to add visual explainations to the size of the prison.

Other than that detail and decals can't hurt anything.

This map will quite hopefully be exclusive to the Xtreme jailbreak servers in australia, I don't mind the preveiw versions being used on minor servers since i plan to make the full version something that no other preveiw version will have.
